sequenceDiagram
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant AlertMgr as Alertmanager
    participant PagerDuty as PagerDuty
    participant Slack as Slack
    participant OnCall as On-Call Engineer
    participant Grafana as Grafana
    participant K8s as Kubernetes
    participant App as App Pods

    Prometheus->>Prometheus: Evaluate alert rules (every 15s)
    Prometheus->>AlertMgr: FIRING: HighErrorRate (>5% 5xx for 5min)
    AlertMgr->>AlertMgr: Group + deduplicate
    
    par Route to channels
        AlertMgr->>PagerDuty: trigger incident (P1)
        PagerDuty-->>OnCall: Page: SMS + phone call
    and
        AlertMgr->>Slack: #incidents: 🔴 HighErrorRate on prod-api
    end

    OnCall->>Grafana: Open dashboard
    Grafana->>Prometheus: query_range(rate(http_5xx[5m]))
    Prometheus-->>Grafana: time series data
    Grafana-->>OnCall: Error spike at 14:32 UTC

    OnCall->>K8s: kubectl get pods -l app=api
    K8s-->>OnCall: 3/5 pods CrashLoopBackOff
    OnCall->>K8s: kubectl logs api-pod-abc123
    K8s-->>OnCall: OOMKilled — memory limit exceeded

    OnCall->>K8s: kubectl rollback deployment/api
    K8s->>App: Rolling restart (previous image)
    App-->>K8s: All pods healthy
    K8s-->>OnCall: Rollback complete

    Prometheus->>AlertMgr: RESOLVED: HighErrorRate
    AlertMgr->>Slack: #incidents: ✅ HighErrorRate resolved
    AlertMgr->>PagerDuty: resolve incident
    OnCall->>Slack: Postmortem: OOM due to memory leak in v1.2.3
